      • readCSVData

        public static CSVData readCSVData(java.io.File csvFile,
                  java.lang.String label,
                  java.lang.String delimiter)
        Static method for reading a csv file into an instance of CSVData.
        Parameters:
        csvFile - a file containing csv data
        label - a label to identify the File. This label will be appended to the headers in the result file.
        delimiter - the string which is used in the csv file to delimit the data

      • writeCSVData

        public static void writeCSVData(CSVData dataToWrite,
                java.lang.String filePath,
                java.lang.String delimiter)
        Static method for writinga an instance of CSVData to a file.
        Parameters:
        dataToWrite - the CSVData to be written
        filePath - the path of the result file
        delimiter - the string which is used in the resulting csv file to delimit the data
